This installs Qt Core and other non-GUI essentials on Ubuntu 18.04 :

    sudo apt install qtbase5-dev
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Qt Core includes core non-GUI functionality: event loop, string handling, object model, timers, file system access, etc.

Qt Multimedia is a separate Qt module used for:
       Audio and video playback
       Recording
       Camera support
       Media device handling

To use Qt5::Multimedia, you must install it explicitly:

$sudo apt install qtmultimedia5-dev
